{"id": "365190761b5e5cb5f7d7486a04a694822d2569e16ae8e5ca6dd5ada8944ef741", "item_id": "f19e5998a5:0", "text": "This pattern is designed to evaluate different pattern networks based on an index that can be read from various nodes."}
{"id": "39921a740bf2b67802a2042e1f87e9dec566131c2458aba5683e2827ced0d2c3", "item_id": "f19e5998a5:1", "text": "Switch"}
{"id": "39c3be1198a2fddf18d03608348d9cfaf8823d2dda4d5ff13fdb851bd15d29ea", "item_id": "f19e5998a5:2", "text": "Index"}
{"id": "cf8e494f6f5f640e17be30286647a202405bb580123cc9e755d956f7db32826d", "item_id": "f19e5998a5:3", "text": "This float value indicates what part of the network to evaluate and is often read from an attribute. Values are read as:"}
{"id": "a9cc0c5a96d6228c51bca32777cb8a2f6414d85b36012fc20d0778be5a4fa69e", "item_id": "f19e5998a5:4", "text": "-0.5 to 0.49 are input 0"}
{"id": "72058ac6fed68c10556715a22f669a11463035e2bdee712a260fca72e96c1db7", "item_id": "f19e5998a5:5", "text": "0.5 to 1.49 are input 1"}
{"id": "3be9a574ee89250d147b58d8d173f6ca154cf29c10745947a1d1f603c52140b7", "item_id": "f19e5998a5:6", "text": "1.5 to 2.49 are input 2, so on and so forth."}
{"id": "7abc49dfa87bc183179762b87f9914ceadc46c29a5621493a4a91e54d401c1ed", "item_id": "f19e5998a5:7", "text": "Inputs"}
{"id": "50e0a6803268a945e3cf96092c689dfb69db6e1e100ca643db60ec8f808c1ad1", "item_id": "f19e5998a5:8", "text": "Inputs RGB"}
{"id": "e669b24b8b17a5fc40de3fb3ed9708818cb578615435d4c1142dfdb1afc03d61", "item_id": "f19e5998a5:9", "text": "An array of inputs to be evaluated based on the returned index value."}
{"id": "8ced683702e54433f637ade69822138253fce574f27fc528969df59e30d98a25", "item_id": "f19e5998a5:10", "text": "Below is a simple example where each sphere transform is assigned a user attribute as the index, 0.0, 1.0, 2.0. The available colors and their index are Red[0], Green[1], and Blue[2] (three inputs added to the Inputs RGB array)"}
{"id": "411a502c00037c6516932c1422df733338cfafab7ffcd82aab786e1eb3107908", "item_id": "f19e5998a5:11", "text": "The same"}
{"id": "0b927a19ad850e0478120b0976c14eb0d7fe1b0f68a522d61c3c87f0cd80df6e", "item_id": "f19e5998a5:13", "text": "is attached to the three spheres and a"}
{"id": "f10fea6a2ec17bb10b85ccea83fad5b30941f17adc83469c3f3d73bc50b43f37", "item_id": "f19e5998a5:14", "text": "PxrAttribute"}
{"id": "46f61ccdc36567fd4ce5d6ee8077f4c58d52f2d1ba32291238854643ab6348f5", "item_id": "f19e5998a5:15", "text": "node is connected to the Diffuse Color input of the material."}
{"id": "e327716d3d7910d407e6e1809f6c79319b007c61a982dfd0d624046a3b49cc5a", "item_id": "f19e5998a5:16", "text": "The attribute can be whatever name you desire with a Float data type."}
